OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBreezy this
OL,6,Fevening, especially in the north, but
OL,7,Fdry with sunny spells. Remaining
OL,8,Fbreezy overnight with cloud thickening
OL,9,Fin the north and isolated showers into
OL,10,Fthe Peak District towards dawn. Dry
OL,11,Fwith clear spells in the south.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FMostly cloudy at first in
OL,14,Fthe north with isolated showers, but
OL,15,Fsunny spells developing and showers
OL,16,Fdying out. Dry with sunny spells in
OL,17,Fthe south. Rather windy, and feeling
OL,18,Fcool.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
