OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FMostly
OL,6,Fdry, bright and increasingly warm
OL,7,Fduring this period. Perhaps some
OL,8,Fshowers on Monday and Tuesday, but
OL,9,Fwith temperatures potentially becoming
OL,10,Fvery warm.
